<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('./includes/head', { siteTitle: themeConfig.siteName }) %>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="antialiased flex flex-col min-h-screen" id="app">
    <%- include('./includes/header', { hideBorder: true }) %>

    <div class="flex-1">
      <div class="bg-yellow-50">
        <div class="max-w-6xl px-8 pt-24 -pb-48 w-full mx-auto lg:px-12 relative">
          <div class="xl:ml-auto text-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <!-- <img class="h-40 inline-block" src="/media/gridea.png" alt="Gridea"> -->
            </div>
            <h1 class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight relative z-10">
              可以，写博客的那个劲儿又回来了
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 sm:mt-4 sm:text-xl font-thin">
              Gridea 是一个静态博客写作客户端，帮助你更容易地构建并管理博客或任何静态站点。
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
              <a href="#started" class="py-2 pl-4 pr-2 border border-2 border-black bg-black hover:bg-yellow-500 hover:text-gray-900 text-white shadow-lg text-lg mt-16 inline-block mx-4 inline-flex items-center transition duration-300">
                立即开始
                <i class="ri-arrow-right-s-line ml-2"></i>
              </a>
              <a href="https://github.com/getgridea/gridea" target="_blank" class="py-2 pl-2 pr-4 border border-2 border-gray-800 bg-white hover:bg-gray-200 text-black shadow-lg text-lg mt-16 inline-block mx-4 inline-flex items-center transition duration-300">
                <i class="ri-github-line mr-2"></i>
                GitHub
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="shadow-lg mb-4 mt-16 rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-2 border-gray-300">
              <img :src="`/media/images/${activeImage}.jpg`" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-center">
              <div
                class="px-6 py-1 flex text-xs shadow-lg cursor-pointer rounded-tl rounded-bl"
                :class="`${activeImage === 'gridea' ? 'bg-yellow-500 text-gray-900' : 'bg-gray-500 text-white'}`"
                @click="activeImage = 'gridea'"
              >
                <i class="ri-article-line mr-2"></i>
                文章列表
              </div>
              <div
                class="px-6 py-1 flex text-xs shadow-lg cursor-pointer"
                :class="`${activeImage === 'editor' ? 'bg-yellow-500 text-gray-900' : 'bg-gray-500 text-white'}`"
                @click="activeImage = 'editor'"
              >
                <i class="ri-edit-circle-line mr-2"></i>
                编辑器
              </div>
              <div
                class="px-6 py-1 flex text-xs shadow-lg cursor-pointer rounded-tr rounded-br"
                :class="`${activeImage === 'theme-setting' ? 'bg-yellow-500 text-gray-900' : 'bg-gray-500 text-white'}`"
                @click="activeImage = 'theme-setting'"
              >
                <i class="ri-settings-line mr-2"></i>
                主题设置
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 为什么你会喜欢使用 Gridea -->
      <div class="bg-white -mt-48 pt-48">
        <div class="max-w-6xl px-8 py-24 w-full mx-auto lg:px-12">
          <h2 class="text-center font-semibold text-4xl mb-24">
            <div class="inline-block">
              为什么你会喜欢使用 Gridea<span class="text-purple-500 absolute">。</span>
              <div class="w-16 bg-purple-500 rounded-sm mt-2" style="height: 2px;"></div>
            </div>
          </h2>
          <div class="flex justify-between flex-wrap">
            <div class="text-center w-full md:w-1/3 px-3">
              <img src="/media/images/markdown.svg" class="w-32 h-32 inline-block">
              <div class="text-xl font-medium py-2">Markdown</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">知道你钟爱 Markdown 写作，我们也是</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center w-full md:w-1/3 px-3">
              <img src="/media/images/safe.svg" class="w-32 h-32 inline-block">
              <div class="text-xl font-medium py-2">快且安全</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Gridea 所有文件都在你的本地，构建为更快更安全的静态网站，无需管理数据库，向 Wordpress 说拜拜</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center w-full md:w-1/3 px-3">
              <img src="/media/images/simple.svg" class="w-32 h-32 inline-block">
              <div class="text-xl font-medium py-2">简而不凡</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">简单几步即可搭建网站。无论博客抑或企业站点，强大的自定义能力，轻松驾驭</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-16 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-thin">还有你搭建网站最关心的(部分功能需要主题支持)：</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-thin mt-1 text-gray-500">
              主题、封面图、标签、菜单、多平台部署、评论、多语言、RSS、KaTeX 公式、Google Analytics、社交链接、TOC...
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 主题 -->
      <div class="bg-yellow-50">
        <div class="max-w-6xl px-8 py-24 w-full mx-auto lg:px-12">
          <h2 class="text-center font-semibold text-4xl mb-24">
            <div class="inline-block">
              主 题<span class="text-pink-500 absolute">。</span>
              <div class="w-16 bg-pink-500 rounded-sm mt-2" style="height: 2px;"></div>
            </div>
          </h2>
          <div class="mt-16">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap">
              <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 pb-8 px-2 md:px-8">
                <img src="/media/images/theme-walker.jpg" alt="" class="box-shadow rounded-sm transition duration-1000 transform hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-lg">
              </div>
              <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 pb-8 px-2 md:px-8">
                <img src="/media/images/theme-tech.jpg" alt="" class="box-shadow rounded-sm transition duration-1000 transform hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-lg">
              </div>
              <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 pb-8 px-2 md:px-8">
                <img src="/media/images/theme-rocky.jpg" alt="" class="box-shadow rounded-sm transition duration-1000 transform hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-lg">
              </div>
              <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 pb-8 px-2 md:px-8">
                <img src="/media/images/theme-line.jpg" alt="" class="box-shadow rounded-sm transition duration-1000 transform hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-lg">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center mt-8">
              <a href="/themes/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-pink-500 text-white inline-block mx-auto shadow-lg inline-flex items-center">
                <i class="ri-t-shirt-line mr-2"></i>
                浏览更多
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 更多人选择 -->
      <div>
        <div class="max-w-6xl px-8 py-24 w-full mx-auto lg:px-12">
          <h2 class="text-center font-semibold text-4xl mb-24">
            <div class="inline-block">
              更多人选择<span class="text-orange-500 absolute">。</span>
              <div class="w-16 bg-orange-500 rounded-sm mt-2" style="height: 2px;"></div>
            </div>
          </h2>
          <div class="text-center text-xl">
            已经有超过 <span class="text-3xl text-orange-500">3,458</span> 位小伙伴使用 Gridea 成功搭建了自己的站点
          </div>
          <div class="text-center text-xs text-gray-600 mt-8">统计数据非实时更新。</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 选择你的版本 -->
      <div class="bg-yellow-50">
        <div class="max-w-6xl px-8 py-24 w-full mx-auto lg:px-12" id="started">
          <h2 class="text-center font-semibold text-4xl mb-24">
            <div class="inline-block">
              选择你的版本<span class="text-green-500 absolute">。</span>
              <div class="w-16 bg-green-500 rounded-sm mt-2" style="height: 2px;"></div>
            </div>
          </h2>
          <div class="mt-16 flex justify-center flex-col md:flex-row">
            <a
              :href="`https://github.com/getgridea/gridea/releases/download/v${version}/Gridea-${version}.dmg`"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-xl px-4 py-2 text-center inline-flex items-center justify-center mb-8 md:mb-0 item bg-black text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-black mx-4 shadow-lg transition duration-300"
            >
              <i class="ri-apple-line mr-2"></i> Mac OS
            </a>
            <a
              :href="`https://github.com/getgridea/gridea/releases/download/v${version}/Gridea.Setup.${version}.exe`"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-xl px-4 py-2 text-center inline-flex items-center justify-center mb-8 md:mb-0 bg-blue-500 text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-500 mx-4 shadow-lg transition duration-300"
            >
              <i class="ri-windows-line mr-2"></i> Windows
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/getgridea/gridea/releases"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-xl px-4 py-2 text-center inline-flex items-center justify-center mb-8 md:mb-0 bg-orange-500 text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-orange-500 mx-4 shadow-lg transition duration-300"
            >
              <i class="ri-ubuntu-line mr-2"></i> Linux
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center text-sm mt-8 text-gray-600">
            当前版本: v{{ version }}
            <a href="https://github.com/getgridea/gridea/releases" target="_blank" class="ml-2 text-blue-500">✨ What's new?</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('./includes/footer') %>
  </div>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/vue/dist/vue.js"></script>
  <script src="/media/scripts/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>